% ================================================
% Legal References (APA 11.4-11.10)
% APA 7th Edition Chapter 11 - Legal References
% ================================================
% 
% This file contains examples for legal reference citations:
% - Court cases and judicial decisions
% - Legislation and statutes
% - Constitutional references
% - Legal administrative materials
% - Patents and legal documents
% - International treaties
% 
% Usage: Legal references have special formatting requirements.
% Use CITATION field for legal citations, LOCATION for statute references.
% ================================================

% (APA 11.4 Example 1) - Court case
@JURISDICTION{11.4:1,
